# CHANGELOG

All notable changes to this project are documented here.  
This changelog mirrors the commit history from GitHub.

---

## [1.0.0] - 2025-10-18
### Added
- Initial project setup with Expo.
- Created `App.js` base structure.
- Added basic layout for menu input fields and dish list.

---

## [1.1.0] - 2025-10-19
### Added
- Implemented splash screen with fade-in animation.
- Added navigation logic to move from splash to main app screen.
- Updated background color and centered text for improved UI.

---

## [1.2.0] - 2025-10-20
### Added
- Added “Add New Dish” feature for chefs.
- Enabled display of added dishes using `FlatList`.
- Added form validation to prevent empty fields.
- Introduced filter options for dish categories.

---

## [1.3.0] - 2025-10-20
### Updated
- Improved layout and typography for better readability.
- Adjusted button styling for consistency with app theme.
- Fixed issue with uncentered elements on smaller screens.

---

## [1.4.0] - 2025-10-20
### Added
- Implemented a total screen that sums up the total number of dishes and money.
- Added Logout button (returns user to Splash screen).
- Finalized single-file navigation and UI polish.

---

## [1.5.0] - 2025-10-21
### Final Touches
- Create a link to the git repository.
- Created `CHANGELOG.md` to mirror GitHub commits.
- Tested app functionality on emulator and Android device.
